ount. <br />\n<br />\n4) Bond Covenant and Due Diligence, do you know if you bought a convertible bond that could turn into a share if the market deteriorate."},{"pid":"499e4cca0913a08873675e28916b9736a403ad6c","tid":2011420,"uid":239912,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T04:07:19.000Z","msg":"不如直接d<br />\n假設：我咩都贏<br />\ntopic已完"},{"pid":"84100d763fe0777b6e7cafd7403e4ef2b667d120","tid":2011420,"uid":42879,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T04:09:01.000Z","msg":"其實到你年年比人加租唔續租搬多幾次你就明，始終要有間自己既地方⋯"},{"pid":"5083bd13a8f8b54b16bbf0a6b03b14fe36eb321c","tid":2011420,"uid":61770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"145afbe5707d0090361831764a58d43b08b8d77f","tid":2011420,"uid":34612,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T03:58:17.000Z","msg":"過咗一年，樓主賺咗12萬未？ 定係賺更多？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T04:10:05.000Z","msg":"Post 1 講過<br />\n唔只10% <br />\n個陣係二月"},{"pid":"2ac915d941b80941eba87f1656cd356372f78f80","tid":2011420,"uid":60082,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T04:54:35.000Z","msg":"假設自己係股神就梗係租樓<br />\n現實係9成股民都只係自以為自己係股神..."},{"pid":"683cf5ddf6baeaf478942b60ecb195e981900468","tid":2011420,"uid":61770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ac915d941b80941eba87f1656cd356372f78f80","tid":2011420,"uid":60082,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T04:54:35.000Z","msg":"假設自己係股神就梗係租樓<br />\n現實係9成股民都只係自以為自己係股神..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T05:42:47.000Z","msg":"正確"},{"pid":"b34eeaa3e11e45c7e68df1025f661d356bcca0e4","tid":2011420,"uid":55400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T07:09:26.000Z","msg":"個百二萬追到通帳未<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf75875967be8977e71d8b96c1854e1dba8bf108","tid":2011420,"uid":159313,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T07:20:08.000Z","msg":"同d人係賭場贏幾次錢就諗可以靠賭為生<br />\n計晒