 bond price fluctuate based on the market situation. you are not likley hold to maturity, and might sell deep into discount. <br />\n<br />\n4) Bond Covenant and Due Diligence, do you know if you bought a convertible bond that could turn into a share if the market deteriorate."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T14:19:31.000Z","msg":"3) well it isn&rsquo;t clear if he&rsquo;s talking about coupon or ytm, he might even be sitting pretty in some cases.  Tho I agree the market seems to be heading towards a tumultuous direction.<br />\n<br />\n4) I assume he&rsquo;d have done a bit of due diligence if he&rsquo;s investing such a large sum of money. Or am I assuming too much"},{"pid":"710d31434e85470ada27e420385dbf2e39e92431","tid":2011420,"uid":18210,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4585b050306485eef361df9baa554bcbeb233cb2","tid":2011420,"uid":199670,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T12:54:39.000Z","msg":"呢啲post真係害人不淺<br />\n比你地呃左去租一世樓真係慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T14:28:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"273db8f18e8a6b3a07465886b0bd8672a91d6611","tid":2011420,"uid":233193,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"710d31434e85470ada27e420385dbf2e39e92431","tid":2011420,"uid":18210,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4585b050306485eef361df9baa554bcbeb233cb2","tid":2011420,"uid":199670,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T12:54:39.000Z","msg":"呢啲post真係害人不淺<br />\n比你地呃左去租一世樓真係慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T14:28:08.000Z","msg":"<img s